The Eagle Ford shale in South Texas region  




			  In our South Texas region we have proved oil and gas reserves of 9 
			  million barrels of oil equivalent, which is 6% of our total 
			  reserves. We have 19,000 net acres prospective for Eagle Ford 
			  shale development primarily in McMullen and LaSalle counties, 
			  Texas where we have 189 producing wells and potential locations to 
			  drill an additional 336 wells.










