EAGLEFORD SHALE
HAYNESVILLE SHALE
TUSCALOOSA MARINE SHALE








 
The Tuscaloosa Marine shale and other regions  
We have 81,500 net acres prospective for the Tuscaloosa Marine shale play in Mississippi and Louisiana. Our acreage is located in the most active part of this emerging unconventional oil play. We drilled one successful well in this play during 2014, but have suspended drilling in this area until oil prices improve. We have 10 Bcfe in the San Juan basin, Mid-Continent and other areas. Our properties in the other regions accounted for 3% of 2015 daily production at 5 MMcfe per day. 








